<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <main>
            <section class="page-header">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1>Our Institutions</h1>
                    <p>Nageshwaram Foundation Trust is dedicated to fostering educational excellence through its growing
                        network of institutions.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="content-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 50px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 80px;">
                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <img src="/images/school-building.png" alt="N.R.K. Public School"
                                style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);">
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex: 1; align-self: center; min-width: 300px;">
                            <h2 style="color: var(--primary-blue);">N.R.K. Public School</h2>
                            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">A Pillar of
                                Quality School Education</h3>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">N.R.K. Public School, nestled in Shastri Nagar, Batiya,
                                Jamui, Bihar, stands as a testament to our commitment to foundational education. Since
                                its inception, the school has been a beacon of learning, providing a nurturing
                                environment for students from pre-nursery to higher secondary levels. We focus on a
                                comprehensive curriculum that not only excels in academics but also emphasizes character
                                development, sports, and extracurricular activities.</p>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Our dedicated faculty, modern facilities, and
                                student-centric approach ensure that every child receives personalized attention and the
                                opportunity to unlock their full potential.</p>
                            <a href="/school" class="cta-button primary">Visit N.R.K. Public School Website</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row" style="display: flex; gap: 50px; flex-wrap: wrap-reverse;">
                        <div style="flex: 1; align-self: center; min-width: 300px;">
                            <h2 style="color: var(--primary-blue);">Future College Integration</h2>
                            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-gold); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">Expanding Our
                                Educational Horizon</h3>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Building on the success and strong foundation laid by N.R.K.
                                Public School, Nageshwaram Foundation Trust is ambitiously planning to establish a
                                state-of-the-art college. This new institution will aim to provide advanced education
                                and vocational training programs, catering to the growing aspirations of our youth in
                                rural areas.</p>
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 30px;">The college will focus on offering courses that are relevant
                                to emerging industries, equipped with modern laboratories, experienced faculty, and
                                industry partnerships to ensure our students are job-ready.</p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="cta-button secondary">Inquire About Future Plans</a>
                        </div>
                        <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 300px;">
                            <div style="position: relative;">
                                <span
                                    style="position: absolute; top: 20px; right: 20px; background: var(--accent-gold); color: white; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; z-index: 2;">COMING
                                    SOON</span>
                                <img src="/images/college-building.png" alt="Future College"
                                    style="width: 100%; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); opacity: 0.9;">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>